changeSet.sql:
COMMENT ON COLUMN field_mapping.array_source_path IS
    'Source array to iterate, e.g. "lines" or "headerAttributes" (object treated as 1-item array). Empty string = scalar mapping, not part of a repeating block.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN field_mapping.array_target_path IS
    'Target array this row belongs to, e.g. "ContractLine" or "ContractHeaderFlexfieldVA". Empty string = scalar mapping. Must be set together with array_source_path.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN field_mapping.is_singleton_array IS
    'True when the source is a single object (not an array) that should still produce exactly one target array element, e.g. Oracle descriptive flexfield contexts (headerAttributes -> ContractHeaderFlexfieldVA[0]).';
